<br>
Yet, I constantly hear complaints about &quot;there aren't enough lower level raids&quot;. Hmm, the reason there isn't, is that NO ONE SHOWS UP. Only on rare occassions, when the raid is to an already overcamped, mega popular place (I.E - Crystal Caverns - great place) will people turn out in force. <br>
<br>
And, how disrespectful, and downright rude is it to post that you will be there, and then you don't show up? Or, you log in at the time the raid is suppose to start, to begin getting there. <br>
<br>
It really isn't worth it to lead mid level or lower raids.<br>
<br>
Later!<br>
<br>
Bendi Witherspoon<br>
